hopobject.body: Will I get paid for overtime? apothecanna pain cream review Other key findings in the research suggested that this year's summer holiday spending in the north of the country was likely to be up by £118 per person (from £851 to £969) and that nearly a third of all northerners plan to spend more than £1,000 per person this summer. Some 30 per cent of all Scots also plan to spend more than £1,000 on a summer holiday with only one in five southerners thinking of doing likewise.
